and\n| CD, download\n|-\n| ''Moon Breakers''\n| June 19, 2012<ref>{{cite web|title=Moon Breakers \u2013 EP| url= https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/moon-breakers-ep/id537908481| publisher=  iTunes Store|accessdate=November 21, 2013}}</ref>\n| Conan the Furky\n| Download\n|-\n| ''[[Defiance (video game)|Defiance]]''\n| April 2, 2013<ref>{{cite web|title=Defiance (Original Video Game Soundtrack)| url= https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/defiance-original-video-game/id627116362| publisher=  iTunes Store|accessdate=November 21, 2013}}</ref>\n| Sparks and Shadows\n| Download\n|-\n| ''[[Assassin's Creed Syndicate#Jack the Ripper DLC|Assassin's Creed Syndicate: Jack the Ripper]]''\n| December 15, 2015<ref>{{cite web|title=Assassin's Creed Syndicate: Jack the Ripper (Original Game Soundtrack) \u2013 EP| url= https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/assassins-creed-syndicate/id1061258124| publisher=  iTunes Store|accessdate=January 8, 2015}}</ref>\n| Ubisoft Music\n| Download (EP)\n|-\n|''[[God of War (2018 video game)|God of War]]''\n|April 13, 2018<ref>{{cite web|title=God of War (PlayStation Soundtrack)| url= https://www.amazon.com/God-PlayStation-Soundtrack-Bear-McCreary/dp/B07C2D3SRG/| publisher= Amazon|accessdate=May 2, 2018}}</ref>\n|Sony Classical\n|CD, download\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Singles ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" \n! Title\n! Year\n! Album\n|-\n| \"Temporal Distortion\"<ref>{{cite web|title=Temporal Distortion \u2013 Single | url= https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/temporal-distortion-single/id504866157|work=Apple Inc.| publisher= iTunes Store|accessdate=November 21, 2013}}</ref>\n| 2012\n| \n|-\n| \"You Are My Home\"<span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring Brendan McCreary)</span><ref>{{cite web|title=You Are My Home (feat. Brendan McCreary) \u2013 Single| url= https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/you-are-my-home-feat.-brendan/id542182910|work=Apple Inc.| publisher= iTunes Store|accessdate=June 29, 2014}}</ref>\n| 2012\n| \n|-\n| \"Da Vinci's Demons\"<span style=\